## API 参考

### Avatar Props

::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: src
    description: '头像图片地址'
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
  - name: alt
    description: '图片替代文本'
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
  - name: name
    description: '名称（用于生成首字母 fallback）'
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
  - name: icon
    description: 'icon 名称（基于 TxIcon）'
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
  - name: size
    description: '头像尺寸'
    type: "'small' | 'medium' | 'large' | 'xlarge'"
    default: "'medium'"
  - name: status
    description: '状态'
    type: "'online' | 'offline' | 'busy' | 'away'"
    default: '-'
  - name: clickable
    description: '是否可点击'
    type: 'boolean'
    default: 'false'
  - name: backgroundColor
    description: '自定义背景色'
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
  - name: textColor
    description: '自定义文字色'
    type: 'string'
    default: '-'
---
::

### Avatar Events

::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: click
    description: '点击头像时触发（仅 clickable=true）'
    type: '() => void'
    default: '-'
---
::

### Avatar Slots

::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: default
    description: '自定义头像内容（优先级高于 icon/name）'
    type: '-'
    default: '-'
---
::
